has-[.block-title]:pt-0 col-span-full lg:col-span-4 gap-8 flex flex-col xl:pt-[52px] lg:pt-12 pt-0"><div id="block5269609"><div id="block-title" class="block-title flex items-end gap-1"><h2 class="font-bold text-teal-500 after:content-[''] after:size-2 after:inline-block after:bg-current after:ml-1 mb-4 text-2xl xl:text-3xl">Neofeed</h2></div><div id="neofeeddiv"></div>

<script>
  setTimeout(() => {
    fetch(`${cnnbr_globals.home_url}/wp-json/cnn-feeds/v1/neofeed`)
      .then((response) => response.json())
      .then((response) => renderNeoFeedBlock(response))
      .catch((err) => console.error(err));
  }, 1500);

  function renderNeoFeedBlock(content) {
    const blockElementId = document.querySelector("#block5269609");
    const blockElementParent =
      document.getElementById("neofeeddiv")?.parentElement.parentElement
        .parentElement.parentElement;

    const blockElement = blockElementId ?? blockElementParent;

    const blockWrapper = `
        <section id="block-neofeed" class="block block--editorial accent--economy">
        	<div class="container">
        		<ul class="block__news__list">
        		</ul>
        	</div>
        </section>
    `;

    blockElement.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", blockWrapper);
    renderNeoFeedPosts(content);
  }

  function renderNeoFeedPosts(posts) {
    let postElements = "";
    const neoFeedBlock = document.querySelector(
      "#block-neofeed .block__news__list"
    );

    posts.forEach(function (post, postKey) {
      const maxPosts = location.pathname.includes("/economia") ? 6 : 2;
      if (postKey >= maxPosts) return;

      const thumbClass =
        postKey === 0
          ? "block__news__thumb--highlight group relative w-full from-black/0 to-black"
          : "group flex grow shrink-0 h-auto flex-row items-center lg:flex-row lg:items-center gap-4 relative";

      const thumbImgClass = postKey === 0 ? "w-full h-72" : "w-32 h-28";

      const gradientElement =
        postKey === 0
          ? '<span class="absolute top-0 block h-full w-full rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-b"></span>'
          : "";

      const listItemClass =
        postKey === 0 ? "mb-4" : "border-t border-neutral-300 py-4";

      const captionClass =
        postKey === 0
          ? "absolute bottom-0 z-10 mb-4 w-full content-end px-4 text-white"
          : "";

      const titleClass =
        postKey === 0
          ? "font-medium xl:text-2xl text-xl"
          : "text-base font-bold flex w-fit hover:underline";

      const badgeElement =
        postKey === 0
          ? ""
          : '<span class="hide__l font-regular overflow-hidden absolute left-0 top-0 min-h-3 min-w-6 px-2 py-1 text-center text-xs text-white bg-teal-500 rounded-ss-lg [#manchete-section-one_&]:hidden [#manchete-section-one_&]:md:block"></span>';

      postElements += `
            <li class="block__news__item has--thumb ${listItemClass}">
                <a href="${post.link}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
                    <figure class="block__news__thumb ${thumbClass}">
                        ${gradientElement}
                        ${badgeElement}
                        <img class="flex object-cover overflow-clip rounded-md ${thumbImgClass}" loading="lazy" alt="${post.title}" src="${post.thumb}">
                        <figcaption class="${captionClass}">
                            <h3 class="block__news__title ${titleClass}">${post.title}</h3>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </a>
            </li>
       `;
    });

    neoFeedBlock.insertAdjacentHTML("beforeend", postElements);
  }
</script>
